column2: SELECT s.specObjID as specObjID, m.ra AS ra, m.dec AS dec, s.h_beta_flux as h_beta, s.oiii_#_flux as OIII, s.h_alpha_flux as h_alpha, s.nii_#_flux as NII into mydb.SDSS_SIMARD_ALL_FLUXES from MyDB.SDSS_SIMARD_ALL_RADEC AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjAllEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS s ON n.specObjID = s.specObjID
